spec_data.Name: php-firebase-php-jwt
spec_data.Description:
A simple library to encode and decode JSON Web Tokens (JWT) in PHP, conforming
to RFC 7519 [1].

Autoloader: /usr/share/php/Firebase/JWT/autoload.php

[1] https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519
